convertToAssets(uint256).details: Calculates the asset value for an amount of shares / tranche tokens provided. The calcultion is based on the token price from the most recent epoch retrieved from Centrifuge chain.

convertToShares(uint256).details: Calculates the amount of shares / tranche tokens that any user would get for the amount of assets provided. The calcultion is based on the token price from the most recent epoch retrieved from Centrifuge chain.

deposit(uint256,address).details: collect shares for deposited funds after pool epoch execution. maxMint is the max amount of shares that can be collected. Required assets must already be locked maxDeposit is the amount of funds that was successfully invested into the pool on Centrifuge chain

file(bytes32,address).details: investmentManager and asset address to be filed by the factory on deployment

returns._0: Maximum amount of stable currency that can be deposited into the Tranche by the receiver after the epoch had been executed on Centrifuge chain.

maxMint(address).details: Maximum amount of shares that can be claimed by the receiver after the epoch has been executed on the Centrifuge chain side.

maxRedeem(address).details: Max amount of shares that can be redeemed by the owner after redemption was requested

mint(uint256,address).details: collect shares for deposited funds after pool epoch execution. maxMint is the max amount of shares that can be collected. Required assets must already be locked maxDeposit is the amount of funds that was successfully invested into the pool on Centrifuge chain

returns.shares: that any user would get for an amount of assets provided -> convertToShares

returns.assets: that any user would get for an amount of shares provided -> convertToAssets
that any user could redeem for an given amount of shares -> convertToAssets

returns.shares: that a user would need to redeem in order to receive the given amount of assets -> convertToAssets

redeem(uint256,address,address).details: Redeem shares after successful epoch execution. Receiver will receive assets for the exact amount of redeemed shares from Owner after epoch execution.

returns.assets: currency payout for the exact amount of redeemed _shares

requestDeposit(uint256).details: request asset deposit for a receiver to be included in the next epoch execution. Asset is locked in the escrow on request submission

requestRedeem(uint256).details: request share redemption for a receiver to be included in the next epoch execution. Shares are locked in the escrow on request submission

setPoolDetails(uint64,bytes16).details: Centrifuge chain pool information to be filed by factory on deployment

totalAssets().details: The total amount of vault shares

returns._0: Total amount of the underlying vault assets including accrued interest

withdraw(uint256,address,address).details: Withdraw assets after successful epoch execution. Receiver will receive an exact amount of _assets for a certain amount of shares that has been redeemed from Owner during epoch execution.

returns.shares: that have been redeemed for the excat _assets amount
